input.message:
Welcome to Bellini Coatings! I'm glad to hear you'll be joining us soon.

However, information about our time tracking system and internal procedures is part of our confidential employee documentation and is only accessible to current employees through our internal systems.

Once you officially join and receive your employee credentials, you'll have access to our internal wiki where you can find detailed documentation about time tracking, including where to log your hours and why we track time.

In the meantime, if you have questions about onboarding or need general information before your start date, please contact our Human Resources department directly. They'll be happy to help you prepare for your first day!
